Resource Profile: Profile Tumor Measurment

Official URL: https://www.vision-zero-oncology.de/fhir/StructureDefinition/tumor-measurement Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2023-11-02 Computable Name: TumorMeasurement

Copyright/Legal: CC-BY-SA-4.0

Profile for recording measurements of a tumor like the longest diameter or volume. The resource can be used for different measurement methods (e.g. methods in pathology, radiology or physical exams).

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Observation/tumor-size-pathology and Observation/tumor-size-radiology

Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
